rows.label: bf11560100_0010
rows.name:
Hello, partner.
This is a first.

rows.label: bf11560100_0020
rows.name: Metsu...

rows.label: bf11560100_0030
rows.name: So this is the Grail... Metsu...

rows.label: bf11560100_0040
rows.name: He has an awesome presence...

rows.label: bf11560100_0045
rows.name: We would do well to proceed with caution...

rows.label: bf11560100_0050
rows.name: Agreed...

rows.label: bf11560100_0060
rows.name:
Your MO is different this time, Metsu.
What are you trying to do?

rows.label: bf11560100_0070
rows.name: If this is a joke, it's not funny.

rows.label: bf11560100_0080
rows.name: I got bored of it.

rows.label: bf11560100_0090
rows.name: ...Bored?

rows.label: bf11560100_0100
rows.name: Letting Siren have all the fun got old, I mean.

rows.label: bf11560100_0110
rows.name:
I wanted to see the humans dance.
The dance of death, in the flames of hellfire.

rows.label: bf11560100_0120
rows.name: What do you...?

rows.label: bf11560100_0130
rows.name: That.

rows.label: bf11560100_0140
rows.name:
I know full well what 
the Iiran Divine Beast truly is

rows.label: bf11560100_0150
rows.name:
I've decided... I'm gonna lay that truth bare,
for everyone to see.

rows.label: bf11560100_0160
rows.name: Metsu... Bastard!

rows.label: bf11560100_0170
rows.name: Each of the Devices I command...

rows.label: bf11560100_0180
rows.name:
...holds ether energy that would rival
even the largest Divine Beast.

rows.label: bf11560100_0190
rows.name:
Imagine if a legion of them made it to the core of
the Iiran Divine Beast and unleashed that energy all at once...

rows.label: bf11560100_0200
rows.name: Our time for dancing would be short, but sweet.

rows.label: bf11560100_0210
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Guh!

rows.label: bf11560100_0220
rows.name: You want me to stop?

rows.label: bf11560100_0225
rows.name: Had enough? Then try and make me.

rows.label: bf11560100_0230
rows.name: C'mon. Come at me!
